audioanalyze.quickdescript: Transcribes audio/video to text, supports audio/video and links (youtube, twitter, instagram)

downloader.quickdescript: Downloads a video/audio from social platforms (YouTube, Twitter, Instagram)

lyricfinder.quickdescript: Fings lyrics for a song from music platforms (YouTube, Spotify, SoundCloud)

riodejaneiro.quickdescript: Adds a Rio De Janeiro instagram filter over image/video

toaudio.quickdescript: Converts a video or other audio files to a mp3

togif.quickdescript: Converts a video/image to a gif

toimage.quickdescript: Converts all video frames/first frame to image/s

tovideo.quickdescript: Converts a gif to a video
